mentions.tacticalSituation: Putney is a MARGINAL. Tories ahead of Labour by only 1,766 votes.

housing.content: In the past three months, Putney Tories have given the go-ahead for Bloomberg Place in the Riverside Quarter... That's 271 in the Osiers Gate site that will add to the Thames Water sewage works opposite Earl Spencer's Althorp Estate and cause railway and traffic congestion... Labour's Chris Wills: 'This area needs to improve, but not to saturation. We need to work through what we want to see rather than letting it happen around us.'

images.caption: Labour’s Stuart King sets out his Priorities for Putney
